fields.name: DestinationAccountId
fields.description: The name of destination storage account.

fields.name: DestinationAddress
fields.description: The SAS URL for the destination storage container. It must grant write permission.

fields.name: DestinationStorageLocationId
fields.description: The location ID of the destination storage container.

fields.name: DestinationStorageSubscriptionId
fields.description: The subscription ID of the destination storage container.

fields.name: DestinationType
fields.description: The Continuous Export destination type. This has to be 'Blob'.

fields.name: IsEnabled
fields.description: Set to 'true' to create a Continuous Export configuration as enabled, otherwise set it to 'false'.

fields.name: RecordTypes
fields.description: The document types to be exported, as comma separated values. Allowed values include 'Requests', 'Event', 'Exceptions', 'Metrics', 'PageViews', 'PageViewPerformance', 'Rdd', 'PerformanceCounters', 'Availability', 'Messages'.
